[```\newcommand{\amp}{&}
\begin{aligned}
\sqrt[4]{48}\amp=\sqrt[4]{16\cdot3}\\
\amp=\sqrt[4]{16}\sqrt[4]{3}\\
\amp=2\sqrt[4]{3}
\end{aligned}
```]

This is as simple as we can make this expression.

